  {
    "hotel_id": "10307",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/pudong-shangri-la-east-shanghai/hotel/shanghai-cn.html",
    "name": "Pudong Shangri-La, Shanghai",
    "detail": "as difficult as it can be to travel around china as a non chinese speaker, the hotel staff made it easy to get around, not only showing locations on a map, but drawing an additional map marked with landmarks that would be easy for me to spot. the horizon club lounge was a relaxing oasis. the lounge staff was very attentive and seemed to preempt my every need. it should be noted that they do have a smoking section, but it is not separated by doors. you can smell smoke when you walk into the lounge, but it is not overwhelming. (i guess you have to remember you are in china where smoking is permitted in most places). overall, it was a great experience. i felt like i was in a much smaller boutique hotel with the service that comes with that. i look forward to my next visit to shanghai to stay again at the pudong shangri-la. ",
